data.text:
About Woodleigh Comedy Night #5

A Night of Comedy and Fundraising Auctions

Featuring..

Bob Franklin – Jimeoin, Thank God You’re Here, Melbourne Comedy Festival

& Tom Siegert – FunnyGuys.com.au

plus a whole heap of live and silent auctions to raise those PFG funds.

Saturday 15 August – 6:30pm

Peninsula Community Theatre

Cnr Nepean Hwy & Wilsons Rd Mornington

Put a table together and get to know other families in your child's year level.

Get some big belly laughs from top Australian comedians without having to go to the city and all whilst raising funds for the PFG to assist with the provision of those all important extras!

Win win!

Please note this is an 18 years & over event

BYO Food and Drink, or order one of our delicious platters!

^ Plus Booking Fee
